@model IEnumerable<NMUG.Models.Sponsor>

@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Index";
}

<h2><b>Become a Sponsor!</b></h2>
<p>As of September 2008 we currently have over 140 registered group email list members and 46 paid members.  We average 40+ attendees at each monthly meeting and our website generates 300-500 unique visitors weekly.  NMUG has continually grown since inception in 2006 and is considered by several Microsoft Developer Evangelists to be one of the strongest user groups in the SW region.  Our leadership team's primary focus is on growing the presence in the New Mexico area to help the group gain exposure to more Microsoft events and companies looking for great sponsorship opportunities to Microsoft Developers.</p>
<p>We are a New Mexico Non-Profit corporation; with an IRS 501 (c)(3) application in process.</p>

